                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #CCBFAD\">Invocazione</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Fase finale:</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> infliggi 1 </span><span style=\"color: #FFE699\">DAN da Geo</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">.<br></span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Utilizzi: 2</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Quando questa carta è in campo</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">, la tue Chiori e </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Robobambole di Chiori</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> infliggono </span><span style=\"color: #FFE699\">DAN da Geo</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> +1 (due volte per turno).</span></p>",
